cast.overview: Barbie and Ken are having the time of their lives in the colorful and seemingly perfect world of Barbie Land. However, when they get a chance to go to the real world, they soon discover the joys and perils of living among humans.
cast.title: Barbie

cast.title: The School for Good and Evil

details.biography: Adam Ray is an American comedian, actor, and YouTuber. Known for his versatile comedic talent, Ray has gained recognition for his stand-up, improv, and acting work. Since 2023, he has regularly performed under the persona of "Dr. Phil," a parody of television personality Dr. Phil McGraw, blending sharp humor and impersonation. Ray's work continues to resonate with audiences across various platforms, establishing him as a dynamic presence in the entertainment industry.
details.name: Adam Ray
